\c 14
\s Abhuramu anorwira Roti, uye anosangana naMerikizedheki
\p
\v 1 Zvino nenguva yaAmuraferi, mambo weShinari, naArioki ma­mbo weErasari, naKedhoriraomeri, ma­mbo weEramu, naTidhari, mambo weGoyimi,
\v 2 vakarwa naBhera, mambo weSodhomu, naBherisha, mambo weGomora, naShinabhi, mambo weAdhamu, naShemebheri, mambo weZe­bhoimi, namambo weBhera (rinonziwo Zoari).
\v 3 Ava vose vakasangana mumu­pata weSidhimu (ndiro Gungwa roMu­nyu).
\v 4 Vakanga vava varanda veKedhoriraomeri makore ane gumi namaviri, vakamumukira negore regumi namatatu.
\v 5 Ipapo Kedhoriraomeri wakauya negore regumi namana, namadzimambo aaka­nga anawo, akakunda vaRefaimi paAshitoreti karinaimi, navaZuzimi paHamu, navaEmimi paShave-kiriataimi,
\v 6 navaHori pagomo ravo reSeiri, kusvi­kira paEriparani, pedo nesango.
\v 7 Va­kadzoka, vakasvika Enimishipati (rino­nziwo Kadheshi), vakakunda nyika yose yavaAmareki, navaAmori, vakanga va­gere paHazazoni-tamari.
\p
\v 8 Zvino mambo weSodhomu, nama­mbo weGomora, namambo weAdhamu, namambo weZebhoimi, namambo weBhera (rinonziwo Zoari), vakabuda vaka­gadzira hondo kuzorwa navo pamupata weSidhimu;
\v 9 kuti varwe naKedhorirao­meri, mambo weEramu, naTidhari, ma­mbo weGoyimi, naAmuraferi, mambo weShinari, naArioki, mambo weErasari; madzimambo mana kuti arwe namadzi­mambo mashanu.
\v 10 Zvino mupata weSi­dhimu wakanga uzere namakomba ane tara, madzimambo eSodhomu neGomora vakatiza vakawiramo; vakasara vakatizira kugomo.
\v 11 Vakatora fuma yose yeSo­dhomu neGomora, nezvokudya zvavo zvose, vakaenda.
\v 12 Vakatorawo Roti, mwanakomana womunun'una waAbhu­ramu wakanga agere paSodhomu, ne­fuma yake, vakaenda.
\p
\v 13 Zvino mumwe wakanga apuku­nyuka wakasvika, akaudza Abhuramu, muHebheru; iye wakanga agere pamiti yemiouki yaMamure, muAmori, mu­nun'una waEshikori, munun'una waAneri; ava vakanga vaita sungano naAbhuramu.
\v 14 Zvino Abhuramu wakati achinzwa kuti hama yake yatapwa, akaraira varume vake vakanga vadzidziswa kurwa, vaka­zvarwa paimba yake, vana mazana ma­tatu negumi navasere, akavateverera ku­svikira paDhani;
\v 15 akakamura varwi vake usiku, iye navaranda vake, akavaku­nda, akavateverera kusvikira paHobha, riri kurudyi rweDhamasiko.
\v 16 Akadzosa fuma yose, akadzosawo Roti, hama yake, nefuma yake, navakadziwo nava­nhu.
\v 17 Ipapo mambo weSodhomu waka­buda kundosangana naye pakudzoka kwake pakuuraya Kedhorir-omeri nama­dzimambo akanga anavo pamupata weShave (ndiwo mupata wamambo).
\v 18 Me­rikizedheki, mambo weSaremi, akauya nechingwa newaini; iye waiva mupristi waMwari woKudenga-denga.
\p
\v 19 Akamuropafadza, akati, Abhuramu ngaaropafadzwe naMwari woKudenga­denga, muridzi wokudenga napasi.
\p
\v 20 Mwari woKudenga-denga ngaaku­dzwe, wakapa vavengi venyu mumaoko enyu. Akamupa chegumi chezvose.
\p
\v 21 Zvino mambo weSodhomu akati kuna Abhuramu, Ndipe vanhu, iwe utore hako fuma.
\p
\v 22 Abhuramu akati kuna mambo weSodhomu, Ndakasimudzira ruoko rwa­ngu kuna Jehovha, Mwari woKudenga­denga, muridzi wokudenga napasi,
\v 23 kuti handingatori rushinda kana rukanda rwe­shangu, kana chinhu chimwe chezvinhu zvenyu, kuti murege kuzoti, Ndini nda­kafumisa Abhuramu,
\v 24 ini handidi ha­ngu, asi zvakadyiwa namajaya chete, nomugove wavanhu vakaenda neni, va­naAneri, naEshikori, naMamure, ngava­tore migove yavo.
